These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, 7up, iced-tea, almond-milk, juice
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |       2        |     3     |      4       |   5   |   6    |
| Beverage   | tea | almond-milk | cola | juice | iced-tea | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: aconite, begonia, azalea, daisy, zinnia, amaryllis
1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |   5    |    6    |
| Flower   | daisy | aconite | azalea | amaryllis | zinnia | begonia |

