.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: r&b, trance, ambient, soul, dubstep, techno
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5       |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | trance | ambient | dubstep | r&b | techno | soul |

