.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: soccer, surfing, parkour, skateboarding, lacrosse, handball
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |   3    |    4    |      5      |  6  |
| Sport   | parkour | soccer | handball | surfing | lacrosse | skateboarding |

