3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |     4     |   5    |    6    |
| Pet   | lizard | goat | rabbit | hedgehog | frog | fish |

